title: Questions raised asking if Donald Trump's 'Latina super fan' was a staged plant
text: When Donald Trump held a campaign rally in Las Vegas last Thursday, the highlight of the night ended up being an usually excited supporter. Now questions are being raised as to how legit the incident actually was. youtube.com
